Itu...

97
00:09:08,840 --> 00:09:09,872
Baunya busuk.

98
00:09:10,600 --> 00:09:12,233
Jelas tak biasa.

99
00:09:13,360 --> 00:09:14,473
Ada sedikit

100
00:09:18,120 --> 00:09:19,672
