158
00:14:29,840 --> 00:14:30,840
Bagaimana...

159
00:14:33,399 --> 00:14:34,672
Bagaimana kau tahu hal ini?

160
00:14:35,845 --> 00:14:37,598
Aku Master Kucing
dari Kota Siluman Chang'an.

161
00:14:38,759 --> 00:14:40,039
Dunia fana memang rumit.

162
00:14:40,799 --> 00:14:41,799
Bagaimana jika

163
00:14:44,679 --> 00:14:46,600
kau ikut denganku ke Kota Siluman?

164
00:14:46,600 --> 00:14:49,033
Biar kucarikan kau tubuh di Toko Kulit,

165
00:14:49,033 --> 00:14:50,159
dan membantu kultivasimu.

166
00:14:50,159 --> 00:14:51,600
Akan kupastikan dia dihukum.

167
00:14:52,280 --> 00:14:53,360
Kau akan mendapatkan keadilan.

168
00:15:12,360 --> 00:15:13,360
Kota Siluman?

169
00:15:15,039 --> 00:15:16,039
Master Kucing?

170
00:15:19,759 --> 00:15:21,039
Master,

171
00:15:21,039 --> 00:15:22,406
karena masalahnya sudah selesai,

172
00:15:22,406 --> 00:15:23,879
