Kau bahkan tak punya kekuatan.

182
00:15:52,679 --> 00:15:54,056
Dasar penipu!

183
00:15:59,360 --> 00:16:00,360
Di sana!

184
00:16:03,440 --> 00:16:04,600
Zhen...

185
00:16:04,600 --> 00:16:06,560
Tunggu, bagaimana mereka
bisa menyeberang?

186
00:16:06,560 --> 00:16:08,034
Apa mereka terbang ke sana?

187
00:16:12,759 --> 00:16:13,792
Mustahil.

188
00:16:18,759 --> 00:16:20,480
Ternyata kau hanya mengulur waktu!

189
00:16:20,480 --> 00:16:21,639
Aku akan menyingkirkanmu

190
00:16:21,639 --> 00:16:23,632
sebelum menghadapi mereka, dasar penipu!

191
00:16:37,799 --> 00:16:38,799
