193
00:17:08,080 --> 00:17:09,599
Zhen!

194
00:17:09,599 --> 00:17:10,599
Zhen!

195
00:17:11,319 --> 00:17:12,792
Apa kau terluka, Zhen?

196
00:17:14,480 --> 00:17:16,359
Ikan Kecil!

197
00:17:16,359 --> 00:17:17,480
Ternyata kau jago bertarung.

198
00:17:17,480 --> 00:17:19,359
Kenapa kau tak pernah memberitahuku?

199
00:17:19,359 --> 00:17:22,040
Ketua Mei, ayunan pedangmu luar biasa.

200
00:17:22,040 --> 00:17:23,720
Di mana pedangku, Ketua Mei?

201
00:17:25,400 --> 00:17:28,200
Bagus, kini aku resmi menjadi
pria terlemah di keluarga kita.

202
00:17:29,119 --> 00:17:31,680
Ketua Mei, apa kau bersedia
dipindah ke Pengawal Jinwu?

203
00:17:31,680 --> 00:17:34,480
Apa kau bersedia bergabung
dengan kami, Ketua Mei?

204
00:17:34,480 --> 00:17:36,000
-Ketua Mei.
-Ikan Kecil.

205
00:17:36,000 --> 00:17:37,000
Aku harus pergi.

206
00:17:38,880 --> 00:17:40,960
Ikan Kecil, aku tak percaya
dengan penglihatanku.

207
00:17:40,960 --> 00:17:42,480
Bagaimana caramu melakukannya?

208
00:17:42,480 --> 00:17:43,552
Apa kau bersedia bergabung?

209
00:17:44,240 --> 00:17:46,680
-Maukah kau bergabung?
-Kenapa kau tak mengajakku?

210
00:17:47,333 --> 00:17:49,720
Tuan Muda, ini Resin Tanduk Kirin.

211
00:18:30,160 --> 00:18:31,873
